<body>
Reports unused arguments, variables, or parameters.
<p>Example (PostgreSQL):</p>
<pre><code>CREATE FUNCTION foo(PARAMUSED INT, PARAMUNUSED INT) RETURNS INT AS
$$
BEGIN
    RETURN PARAMUSED;
END
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;</code></pre>
<p>The <code>PARAMUNUSED</code> parameter is not used in the function and might be deleted.</p>
</body>
